@BloggingPlatformAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5199

### 1. POST создать блог

POST {{BloggingPlatformAPI_HostAddress}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first blog post.",
  "category": "Technology",
  "tags": ["Tech", "Programming"]
}

### 2. GET получить блог по ID

GET {{BloggingPlatformAPI_HostAddress}}/posts/1
Accept: application/json